1. install node.js for your platform

    https://nodejs.org/en/download/

2. install required packages

    npm i

3. copy config.json.sample to config.json, and fill in the values appropriate
   for your environment, leave page as "" if you intend to test the homepage

4. download chromedriver from 

    http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html

put the downloaded chromedriver in your $PATH, and make sure it is executable

5. run the tests

    node axe-test.js

6. please send feedbacks to joe.zhou@cpanel.net
